781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b123e8583bf620f8c824c0cb299cdb887783ef15","tid":2123912,"uid":135475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T03:09:42.000Z","msg":"要有心理準備有幾科啲阿Sir唔教要自學<br />\nSem1好mark 定3-4人做Groupmate<br />\n唔係Sem3你做project做到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:44:46.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講多啲？剩係聽書溫notes努力唔夠？"},{"pid":"521f74f91c9bf2e299b13801640365ca748082e4","tid":2123912,"uid":135475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"500c55be13d24e8e18ddb8c314af2ff087542172","tid":2123912,"uid":26781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b123e8583bf620f8c824c0cb299cdb887783ef15","tid":2123912,"uid":135475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T03:09:42.000Z","msg":"要有心理準備有幾科啲阿Sir唔教要自學<br />\nSem1好mark 定3-4人做Groupmate<br />\n唔係Sem3你做project做到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:44:46.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講多啲？剩係聽書溫notes努力唔夠？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T08:07:12.000Z","msg":"Sem2-3有科System Development Project<br />\n係除咗整C# Software之外<br />\n（sem3做，屌佢老母得個半月就要做晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，建議sem2偷跑做）<br />\n仲要交埋documentation （sem2交draft ）<br />\n基本上係sem1, 2, 3 其他科學過大部份嘅都要應用喺個project<br />\n例如Database, UML, Project managment<br />\n可以話係pre FYP 但係呢科題目係學校俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋唔建議死背書，會讀得好辛苦<br />\n（當然一啲Function要背下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\nLab要做齊，唔明就問阿Sir<br />\nsem2,4係有關IT嘅文科，記得聽下邊啲要考<br />\n拉把website有Pastpaper 可以參考吓<br />\n同埋注意語文科 好多killer<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}